00:13:34,041 --> 00:13:35,541
Did you get in touch
with the coast guard?

258
00:13:35,625 --> 00:13:36,791
I can't get through!

259
00:13:36,875 --> 00:13:38,083
It seems like our
transmissions are jammed!

260
00:13:38,166 --> 00:13:40,083
It must be that boat!

261
00:13:42,125 --> 00:13:43,625
[ANNOUNCER A]
Attention, all passengers.

262
00:13:43,708 --> 00:13:45,666
This is an important
announcement.

263
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:48,583
We're experiencing strong
tidal currents and--

264
00:13:48,666 --> 00:13:52,250
[MAI gasps, groans]

265
00:13:52,333 --> 00:13:55,541
[MAI gasps]

266
00:13:55,625 --> 00:13:57,125
What do you want from me?

267
00:13:57,208 --> 00:13:58,666
[MAI grunts]

268
00:14:01,125 --> 00:14:02,291
[MAI gasps]

269
00:14:06,125 --> 00:14:08,958
[MAI gasps, grunts]

270
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,208
[NATSUKI]
Huh?

271
00:14:12,833 --> 00:14:14,833
[NATSUKI]
What?!

272
00:14:14,916 --> 00:14:15,583
[MITOKO]
Hm.

273
00:14:15,666 --> 00:14:16,666
[MAI gasps]

274
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,291
--[NATSUKI gasps]
--[MITOKO shouts]

275
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:22,500
[ALL shout]

276
00:14:22,583 --> 00:14:25,208
[YUICHI grunts]

277
00:14:25,291 --> 00:14:26,250
Can't believe it.

278
00:14:26,333 --> 00:14:27,916
She really punched me hard.

279
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,583
[CREW F]
Hey! What was that noise?!

280
00:14:29,666 --> 00:14:30,625
[CREW G]
It was from mid-ship!

281
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:32,791
[CREW F]
Oh! The infirmary!

282
00:14:32,875 --> 00:14:34,291
[YUICHI]
Huh?

283
00:14:36,833 --> 00:14:38,125
Where'd Mai go?!

284
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:44,291
[MITOKO grunts]

285
00:14:44,375 --> 00:14:46,375
[NATSUKI]
Don't think about it!

286
00:14:46,458 --> 00:14:48,541
You've caused me
enough trouble already.

287
00:14:50,208 --> 00:14:53,083
[MAI grunts]

288
00:14:53,166 --> 00:14:54,500
[gasps]

289
00:14:56,375 --> 00:14:58,916
Those guys are only using
you for their own objective!

290
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,750
Why don't you
understand that?!

291
00:15:00,833 --> 00:15:02,375
[MITOKO grunts]

292
00:15:02,458 --> 00:15:04,041
[NATSUKI] I can't let any
more of them congregate

293
00:15:04,125 --> 00:15:06,625
on Fuka territory.

294
00:15:06,708 --> 00:15:07,541
The Hime!

295
00:15:07,625 --> 00:15:10,458
[MITOKO grunts]

296
00:15:10,541 --> 00:15:11,250
[NATSUKI]
Don't!

297
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:15,166
[MITOKO grunts]

298
00:15:15,250 --> 00:15:16,458
[MAI yelps]

299
00:15:18,583 --> 00:15:20,291
[NATSUKI grunts]

300
00:15:26,583 --> 00:15:28,708
Hime...?

301
00:15:28,791 --> 00:15:30,625
So I guess I'm
wasting my breath?

302
00:15:30,708 --> 00:15:32,125
[grunts]

303
00:15:32,208 --> 00:15:33,625
Sorry to hear that.

304
00:15:33,708 --> 00:15:35,833
'Cause I'll have
to get serious.

305
00:15:37,375 --> 00:15:38,500
[grunts]

306
00:15:40,916 --> 00:15:42,166
[NATSUKI]
Duran!

307
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:48,541
[howls]

308
00:15:48,625 --> 00:15:50,250
[gasps]

309
00:15:50,333 --> 00:15:51,375
[NATSUKI]
Go!

310
00:15:52,416 --> 00:15:57,416
[MITOKO grunts]

311
00:16:04,583 --> 00:16:05,541
[gasps]

312
00:16:07,041 --> 00:16:08,583
[MITOKO grunts, yells]

313
00:16:08,666 --> 00:16:09,791
[MAI yelps]

314
00:16:12,208 --> 00:16:13,875
[YUICHI, CREW A grunt]

315
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:15,666
[YUICHI]
Fire!

316
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:16,708
Stay back!

317
00:16:16,791 --> 00:16:21,041
[alarm buzzes]

318
00:16:21,125 --> 00:16:22,666
[NATSUKI grunts]

319
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:24,875
[MITOKO grunts]

320
00:16:31,833 --> 00:16:33,750
What's going on?

321
00:16:37,625 --> 00:16:40,083
[CAPTAIN A]
Attention passengers.

322
00:16:40,166 --> 00:16:43,750
It appears that a fire has
broken out on the vehicle deck.

323
00:16:43,833 --> 00:16:44,708
Move it, kid!

324
00:16:44,791 --> 00:16:45,916
[YUICHI]
Uh, yeah.

325
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,333
Coming!

326
00:16:47,416 --> 00:16:51,500
[YUICHI gasps]
Hm? It's her!

327
00:16:51,583 --> 00:16:52,250
Hey!

328
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:54,000
[MAI gasps]

329
00:16:54,083 --> 00:16:55,791
[CREW A]
The crew will assist you!

330
00:16:55,875 --> 00:17:00,000
Please remain calm and evacuate
as quickly as possible!

331
00:17:00,083 --> 00:17:01,333
C'mon. Hurry up, you two!

332
00:17:01,416 --> 00:17:02,500
[TAKUMI]
But my sister!

333
00:17:02,583 --> 00:17:04,041
[SHIHO]
I can't find my brother!

334
00:17:04,125 --> 00:17:06,083
I'm sure they got
on another lifeboat!

335
00:17:06,166 --> 00:17:06,750
Now, hurry!

336
00:17:06,833 --> 00:17:07,458
[TAKUMI]
Wait!

337
00:17:07,541 --> 00:17:08,000
[SHIHO]
But Yuichi!

338
00:17:08,083 --> 00:17:09,083
Don't you worry!

339
00:17:09,166 --> 00:17:10,291
[SHIHO]
No!

340
00:17:11,625 --> 00:17:13,083
There you go!

341
00:17:13,166 --> 00:17:15,583
[MAI grunts]

342
00:17:15,666 --> 00:17:17,250
Thanks.

343
00:17:17,333 --> 00:17:19,208
No prob.

344
00:17:19,291 --> 00:17:20,166
[MAI gasps]

345
00:17:20,250 --> 00:17:22,291
[YUICHI gasps]

346
00:17:22,375 --> 00:17:24,208
[MAI sighs]

347
00:17:24,291 --> 00:17:25,291
[gasps]

348
00:17:25,375 --> 00:17:26,666
[YUICHI grunts]

349
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,916
--What was that back there?!
--[YUICHI] Hang on...

350
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,541
[BOTH grunting]

351
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:33,208
Tell me! What happened
a couple of minutes ago!

352
00:17:33,291 --> 00:17:35,333
Would you mind telling me
what you're talking about?

353
00:17:35,416 --> 00:17:37,208
You sure pack a mean punch.

354
00:17:37,291 --> 00:17:38,958
[MAI]
Hm. I know.

355
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:41,916
Consider us even for what
happened earlier, okay?

356
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,333
Sound like a good deal?

357
00:17:43,416 --> 00:17:44,750
What are you talking about?

358
00:17:44,833 --> 00:17:46,291
The sexual harassment.

359
00:17:46,375 --> 00:17:47,791
Would you drop that?!

360
00:17:47,875 --> 00:17:51,125
Yes, I'm going to.
This is what I'm saying.

361
00:17:51,208 --> 00:17:52,791
[YUICHI, MAI pant]

362
00:17:52,875 --> 00:17:54,208
[MAI]
Takumi...

363
00:17:54,291 --> 00:17:57,125
It looks like everyone
abandoned ship in a big hurry.

364
00:17:57,208 --> 00:18:01,000
I'm starting to dread what'll
happen next on this trip.

365
00:18:01,083 --> 00:18:04,583
Hey. What kind of place
is Fuka Academy, anyway?

366
00:18:04,666 --> 00:18:07,250
It's not some kinda creepy
school or anything, is it?

367
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:09,166
You've been watching
too many horror movies.

368
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:11,458
It's just your average
private school.

369
00:18:11,541 --> 00:18:12,625
All right.

370
00:18:12,708 --> 00:18:14,708
Tomorrow's gonna be
a normal school day.

371
00:18:14,791 --> 00:18:16,333
C'mon, let's get outta here.

372
00:18:16,416 --> 00:18:18,875
And don't complain about
losing your stuff!

373
00:18:18,958 --> 00:18:20,208
[gasps]

374
00:18:22,583 --> 00:18:23,750
[gasps]

375
00:18:23,833 --> 00:18:25,666
Aw...

376
00:18:25,750 --> 00:18:27,583
[YUICHI]
Hey, don't do this to me.

377
00:18:27,666 --> 00:18:29,583
C'mon!

378
00:18:29,666 --> 00:18:34,625
[NATSUKI, MITOKO grunting]

379
00:18:38,083 --> 00:18:39,708
That was your
last chance, Hime.

380
00:18:39,791 --> 00:18:41,541
That's it. You are
finished here.

381
00:18:41,625 --> 00:18:44,416
[MAI grunts]
It's gone! I can't find it!

382
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:46,458
It's not here! Where is it?!

383
00:18:46,541 --> 00:18:47,708
What're you asking me for?!

384
00:18:47,791 --> 00:18:48,958
[MAI gasps]

385
00:18:49,041 --> 00:18:50,625
You're looking for what?

386
00:18:50,708 --> 00:18:53,875
[MAI] A little container!
There's medicine in it!

387
00:18:53,958 --> 00:18:58,916
[MITOKO, NATSUKI grunting]

388
00:19:04,333 --> 00:19:06,541
Duran!

389
00:19:06,625 --> 00:19:08,708
Load Silver Cartridge!

390
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,291
[NATSUKI]
Fire!

391
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:18,625
This wouldn't be what
you're looking for...?

392
00:19:18,708 --> 00:19:22,791
[MITOKO grunts]

393
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,375
[MAI gasps]
That's it!

394
00:19:27,375 --> 00:19:28,666
[MAI yelps]

395
00:19:33,041 --> 00:19:37,291
[grunts]

396
00:19:37,375 --> 00:19:38,250
[YUICHI gasps]

397
00:19:38,333 --> 00:19:39,791
[MAI gasps]

398
00:19:39,875 --> 00:19:40,750
[yelps]

399
00:19:40,833 --> 00:19:43,083
[gasps]

400
00:19:43,166 --> 00:19:44,916
[MAI]
Oh my god!

401
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:47,458
[MAI]
Hey!

402
00:19:47,541 --> 00:19:48,625
[YUICHI]
Huh?

403
00:19:48,708 --> 00:19:51,375
Give that to Takumi!
I'm counting on you!

404
00:19:51,458 --> 00:19:54,583
Right! If I can
stay alive, that is!

405
00:19:58,125 --> 00:19:59,500
[MAI]
This is ridiculous!

406
00:19:59,583 --> 00:20:04,291
There's no way I'm going to
die in a place like this!

407
00:20:04,375 --> 00:20:06,333
[gasps]

408
00:20:06,416 --> 00:20:08,833
[MAI grunts]

409
00:20:08,916 --> 00:20:10,666
[MAI]
Huh? What the...?!

410
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,916
[DURAN howls]

411
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:14,333
[gasps, grunts]

412
00:20:17,958 --> 00:20:19,291
Duran!

413
00:20:19,375 --> 00:20:21,166
Those flames!

414
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:26,708
[gasps]
What's this light?!

415
00:20:26,791 --> 00:20:27,250
[NATSUKI]
Hey!

416
00:20:27,333 --> 00:20:28,791
[MAI]
Huh?

417
00:20:28,875 --> 00:20:30,250
[MAI grunts]

418
00:20:31,916 --> 00:20:34,625
[gasps]

419
00:20:34,708 --> 00:20:36,000
[NATSUKI]
So that's what you are.

420
00:20:36,083 --> 00:20:37,541
[MAI]
Huh?

421
00:20:37,625 --> 00:20:41,750
Then I guess... you can see
that star near the moon as well.

422
00:20:41,833 --> 00:20:43,041
Uh...

423
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:46,666
[MAI]
Hm...

424
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:48,166
That stupid fool!

425
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:50,916
It's going exactly the
way they wanted it to!

426
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,208
Hey, girl!

427
00:20:52,291 --> 00:20:55,291
Take my warning.
Don't go to Fuka Academy.

428
00:20:55,375 --> 00:20:56,125
[MAI gasps]

429
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:58,500
If you go, you will die.

430
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,083
[MAI]
Die?

431
00:21:06,291 --> 00:21:08,875
[MAI gasps]
Hm? Oh, no!

432
00:21:08,958 --> 00:21:11,041
[MAI screams]

433
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:17,750
[screams]

434
00:21:23,583 --> 00:21:24,833
[YUICHI gasps]

435
00:21:24,916 --> 00:21:26,541
I think she's still in there!

436
00:21:26,625 --> 00:21:27,333
What?!

437
00:21:27,416 --> 00:21:29,875
[TAKUMI]
No way... Mai!

438
00:21:29,958 --> 00:21:31,583
Mai!

439
00:21:34,875 --> 00:21:36,458
[NAGI yawns]

440
00:21:36,541 --> 00:21:38,458
I thought this wait
would never end.

441
00:21:38,541 --> 00:21:40,000
Unbelievable.

442
00:21:40,083 --> 00:21:42,541
Oh well, it's over.

443
00:21:42,625 --> 00:21:47,041
Mai-Hime plus one, welcome.

444
00:21:47,125 --> 00:21:50,041
And now, on with
the arrangements!

445
00:21:55,541 --> 00:21:58,958
[MAI grunts]

446
00:21:59,041 --> 00:22:01,416
[MAI]
Huh?

447
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:03,875
[MAI gasps]

448
00:22:08,041 --> 00:22:10,916
[gasps]

449
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,708
[MAI]
Where am I?

450
00:22:12,791 --> 00:22:16,458
[STUDENTS murmur]

451
00:22:16,541 --> 00:22:18,208
No way...

452
00:22:19,416 --> 00:22:21,583
--[SHIHO gasps]
--[YUICHI] Look. There she is.

453
00:22:21,666 --> 00:22:23,208
[chuckles]

454
00:22:23,291 --> 00:22:25,916
[MAI shouts]

455
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:30,958
♪


456
00:23:56,916 --> 00:23:59,291
[SHIHO] Hey. I thought this
was supposed to be a steamy,

457
00:23:59,375 --> 00:24:01,666
burning hot story
set in a school.

458
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:04,291
[TAKUMI] It was burning.
The ferry and all those cars.

459
00:24:04,375 --> 00:24:05,833
[SHIHO]
No. That's not what I meant.

460
00:24:05,916 --> 00:24:08,041
[TAKUMI] The next episode
will take place at school.

461
00:24:08,125 --> 00:24:09,666
[SHIHO gasps]
Will there be passion?

462
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:11,208
[TAKUMI]
Yup. Burning passion.

